- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf log:host.
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf observable:hostname.
""" ;
	rdfs:isDefinedBy noria: ;
	rdfs:seeAlso <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hostname> ;
.

